_aChangeLog.text: Added a tunnel at the T-side of A.
Improved T spawn to look better.
Added a hallway at Bombsite B to

_aLatestUpdates._sText:
And the file size of the map is..... drumroll  32.1 MB! The main reason for this is the, well, low lightmaps.

And the navigation mesh is still buggy, but regardless; It's still playable. And i have no skill in editing .nav files.

_sText:
My first map, because why not.

Also, i named this map after the "grid"-like design of the main part of the map, and where is Bombsite A located.

Patches coming soon.... Maybe, maybe soon.
